[PNG image data - 64x64 pixel art of a friendly robot exploring a starry cosmos, created with creative thinking about humanity's future among the stars. The robot features a rounded dome head with a single glowing eye, antenna with a small red beacon, and a boxy body with articulated arms. The color palette uses deep space blues and purples contrasted with warm copper and gold accents on the robot, with bright cyan and white stars scattered across the background. The style blends retro sci-fi aesthetics with modern pixel art techniques, evoking a sense of wonder and peaceful exploration.]